This is part of a group of templates that are used to display astronomical information related to a specific star. It should always be proceded by a {{tl|Starbox begin}} template. The template can then be used as follows:

 {{Starbox astrometry <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   radial_v=''徑向速度'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   prop_mo=''自行'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   pos_ang=''位置角'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   parallax=''視差'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   p_error=''視差誤差'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   dist_ly=''光年的距離'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   dist_pc=''秒差距的距離'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   absmag_v=''絕對星等的結果}}

In addition, the following optional parameters are computed if they are not set:

   dist_ly=''光年的距離'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>
   dist_pc=''秒差距的距離'' <nowiki>|</nowiki>

This template can also be proceded or followed by other Starbox templates:

*{{tl|Starbox image}}
*{{tl|Starbox observe}}
*{{tl|Starbox character}}
*{{tl|Starbox visbin}} 
*{{tl|Starbox detail}}
*{{tl|Starbox catalog}} 

The list should then be closed with a {{tl|Starbox end}} template.
